PM2_expl: PM2_Moderate: gnomAD max AF=0 < threshold 0.0001 for MOI AD
PM4_expl: PM4_Moderate: truncating variant in last exon removing >10% of protein length; do not apply PVS1 for last-exon truncations
PP3_expl: PP3 not applied: variant is LOF/canonical-splice or PVS1 was assigned; computational evidence is not stacked with PVS1/LOF for this pipeline.
PP5_expl: PP5_Supporting: high-quality database annotation (ClinVar≥2★ or HGMD DM≥2 pubs or Internal DB P/LP)
